These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, cola, juice, iced-tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  writer, scientist, social-worker, librarian, nurse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep, hip-hop, classical, pop
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine, indian, canadian, german
 1. the indian is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 2. the writer is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the argentine##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the writer##3
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the nurse is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 8. the german is in an even position##4
 9. the pakistani is on the left or right of the librarian##3
10. the fan of hip-hop is the social-worker##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the writer##3
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the argentine##1
14. the german is on the left of the fan of pop##1
15. the fan of classical is the person drinking juice##1
16. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | cola    | almond-milk   | juice     | iced-tea      | fanta      |
| Job           | social-worker | nurse | writer    | librarian | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | r&b         | classical      | dubstep      | pop    |
| Nationality   | indian    | canadian         | argentine | german  | pakistani   |

