.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, magic-tricks, chess, sudoku
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, dubstep, hip-hop, punk, salsa
5 different pets are kept: cat, goat, bird, dog, pony
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, helicopter, jet-ski, taxi
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of salsa##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person driving the motorbike##2
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
13. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
14. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | chess | camping | magic-tricks   | skydiving | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | dubstep   | salsa    | indie        | punk        |
| Pet           | dog         | pony  | cat  | goat   | bird      |
| Transport     | motorbike        | jet-ski  | helicopter | taxi | airplane         |

