.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, soy-milk, sprite, iced-tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: colasy, romance, drama, crime, comedy
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, skiing, surfing, handball
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, boat, airplane, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
 9. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the boat##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is badminton##1
11. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching colasy movies##2
13. the person watching colasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
