The people use 5 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, boat, bike, airplane
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person driving the train##2
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 4. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating tomato##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 9. the person eating grapefruit is the fan of d&b##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
14. the person eating tomato is the person eating tomato##1
15. the person driving the bike is the person watching documentary movies##1
16. the person eating radish is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
17. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3

.:: Answer ::.
