 3. the chinese is on the far left##1
 4. the canadian is on the left of the indonesian##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking water is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the jet-ski##2
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the dutch##3
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person driving the ship is the chinese##1
12. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
13. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is surfing##1
14. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
15. the person driving the bus is on the right of the chinese##1
16. the person drinking almond-milk is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
