.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-7::.
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, plum, kiwi, spinach, artichoke
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, fantasy, sports, epic
5 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, rabbit, rat, pony
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, handball, cycling, cricket, tennis
 1. the person eating spinach is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 4. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's sport is tennis and the owner of the pony##2
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the rat##2
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person eating plum is the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the person eating pineapple is in the middle##1
11. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
13. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
14. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
15. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
16. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |       3       |     4      |     5      |
