5 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, pony, rat, hedgehog
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, golf, volleyball, badminton, parkour
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the polish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the polish is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the french##3
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person eating orange##2
 9. the colombian is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the colombian is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the colombian is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
13. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
14. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Food          | orange      | cranberry       | strawberry | artichoke | lime |
| Nationality   | french       | malaysian    | polish  | nigerian  | colombian |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | guinea-pig | ferret      | pony     | rat    |
| Sport         | parkour | rowing   | volleyball   | badminton  | golf |

